               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18490226-name-1141" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18490226-name-1141" type="gender" value="indeterminate"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18490226-name-1141" type="surname" value="ASH"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18490226-name-1141" type="given" value="LEWISH"></interp>LEWISH ASH</persName>
                  </hi>. I am an engineer. The prisoner was apprentice to me—he was in my service up to 2d Feb., when he absconded in the morning—about ten o'clock that morning, we missed this ratchet brace—it was safe on a machine in the factory several days before—this is it (<hi rend="italic">produced</hi>).</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Cross-examined by</hi> 
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">MR. BALLANTINE</hi>. <hi rend="italic">Q.</hi> When was he bound appren<lb></lb>tice? <hi rend="italic">A.</hi> On 4th April, for seven years, with a premium of 50<hi rend="italic">l</hi>.—I had to</p>
               <xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="184902260153"></xptr>
               <p>keep him—I have not given back any of the 50<hi rend="italic">l</hi>.—this brace is worth 50<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. or 3<hi rend="italic">l</hi>.—the prisoner's mother is not in want—she has got plenty of money—the prisoner has absconded three times from his apprenticeship, and we have missed property.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18490226-name-1142" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18490226-name-1142" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18490226-name-1142" type="surname" value="HORTON"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18490226-name-1142" type="given" value="RICHARD"></interp>RICHARD HORTON</persName>
                  </hi>. I am in the service of Mr. Duke, a pawnbroker, in Lambeth Marsh. This brace was pawned by the prisoner on 3d Feb.—I did not know him before—I am sure he is the person.</p>
